The paper focuses on security and privacy issues in mobile networks, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR) and computer networks (cs.NI). The methodology used to categorize attacks and defenses also involves software engineering (cs.SE) and system design (cs.SY). Additionally, the paper discusses the impact of attacks on users' privacy, which relates to cybersecurity (cs.CY).
